text:
Home » Features , Travel & Food » Amari Phuket checked in The First Ocean Wing Guests Amari Phuket checked in The First Ocean Wing Guests Written by Phuketindex | July 16, 2015 | 0 | Amari Phuket checked in The First Ocean Wing Guests 
Phuket, 16 July 2015 – The Amari Phuket management team led by Pierre-Andre Pelletier – Vice President and Area General Manager, South Thailand (Left), Richard Margo – Hotel Manager (second from right) and Tipaporn Koonphol (right) recently gave a warm welcome to the Rujevic Family from Australia who were the first Ocean Wing guests. They were the first to experience the brand new product of Amari Phuket.
